In re WISE SHOES, Inc. Fifth Avenue Realty Corporation, Appellant. No. 359. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 3, 1933. Pollock & Nemerov, of New York City (Henry W. Pollock and Maurice J. Dix, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. David W. Kahn and Nathan Friedman, both of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (2 F. Supp. 521) affirmed.
